# Frontend (Shadcn-Svelte)

- **Primitives (vendored)** live in `src/lib/components/ui/*` and are managed by the Shadcn-Svelte CLI.
- **App components** should compose primitives under `src/lib/components/*` (non-`ui/`).
- **Allowed**: if a primitive is **not customized**, use it directly (don't create a wrapper "just because").
- Prefer **composition-first** customization (wrappers/slots/classes) to keep vendor updates easy.
- For vendor refreshes, use a dedicated branch like `chore/ui-vendor-update-YYYY-MM` and update components one-at-a-time with overwrite (review diffs).
- For **translatable UI text**, use the i18n helper `t()` from `$lib/i18n` and keep `src/lib/i18n/messages/*.json` in sync across languages.

See `AGENTS.md` for the detailed workflow.
